                            <comment id="301183" author="eaujames" created="Tue, 11 May 2021 14:51:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have applied the &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/43277&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/43277&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10048&quot; title=&quot;osd-ldiskfs to truncate outside of main transaction&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10048&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10048&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ofd: take local locks within transaction&quot;) + &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/43278&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/43278&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13093&quot; title=&quot;osd_trans_exec_check()) lustre-OST0001: opcode 0: used 8, used now 8, reserved 1 LBUG&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-13093&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-13093&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; osd: fix osd_attr_set race&quot;) on the problematic filesystem. The issue never occurred after.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We were able to reproduce this issue in 5/10 min with many creations of small files and several threads doing file migrations (&quot;lfs migrate&quot; between OSTs).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
